33
00:04:49,500 --> 00:04:51,416
- WITH THAT FOG--

34
00:04:51,500 --> 00:04:53,666
- THAT REMINDS ME OF SOMETHING.

35
00:04:53,750 --> 00:04:57,000
A MAN SAID THE FUTURE
IS AN OPAQUE MIRROR.

36
00:04:57,083 --> 00:04:59,458
ANYONE WHO TRIES
TO LOOK INTO IT SEES NOTHING

37
00:04:59,541 --> 00:05:02,875
BUT THE DIM OUTLINES
OF AN OLD AND WORRIED FACE.

38
00:05:02,958 --> 00:05:05,708
- MY SHIP--
IT'S RIGHT NEARBY.

39
00:05:05,791 --> 00:05:08,875
- THE ANSWERS YOU SEEK
YOU WILL NEVER FIND

40
00:05:08,958 --> 00:05:11,208
UNTIL YOU START
TO LOOK WITHIN YOURSELF.

41
