46
00:05:24,125 --> 00:05:27,375
NOTHING THAT YOU DO
WILL MAKE IT STEEP ANY FASTER.

47
00:05:27,458 --> 00:05:30,958
YOU CAN'T JUST RUN AROUND
TRYING TO DO EVERYTHING AT ONCE.

48
00:05:31,041 --> 00:05:34,958
SO WHY NOT TAKE ADVANTAGE
OF THE BOOKSTORE?

49
00:05:35,041 --> 00:05:37,500
- YEAH.
SORRY FOR BEING IMPATIENT.

50
00:05:37,583 --> 00:05:40,541
I WAS JUST GOING
TO ASK YOU FOR DIRECTIONS.

51
00:05:43,125 --> 00:05:47,250
WELL, IT LOOKS LIKE YOU HAVE
A PRETTY IMPRESSIVE SHOP.

52
00:05:47,333 --> 00:05:49,958
I GUESS I'LL HAVE A LOOK,

53
00:05:50,041 --> 00:05:51,583
MAYBE FIND SOMETHING.

54
