106
00:09:05,625 --> 00:09:08,083
TO OBSERVE
IS TO CREATE PERSPECTIVE.

107
00:09:08,166 --> 00:09:10,583
I CAN NEVER CEASE
TO BE THE POINT OF ORIGIN

108
00:09:10,666 --> 00:09:12,208
FROM MY PERSPECTIVE.

109
00:09:12,291 --> 00:09:15,125
I OBSERVE THAT
WHICH IS NOT MYSELF.

110
00:09:15,208 --> 00:09:17,708
THIS IS THE FIRST PRINCIPLE
DEFINED!

111
00:09:17,791 --> 00:09:19,666
- ( grunting )

112
00:09:23,083 --> 00:09:24,833
- I AM NOBODY.

113
00:09:24,916 --> 00:09:27,166
EVEN IF I WAS SOMEBODY,

114
00:09:27,250 --> 00:09:29,625
I AM BEYOND
YOUR COMPREHENSION.

115
00:09:29,708 --> 00:09:31,625
AND EVEN IF YOU COULD,

116
00:09:31,708 --> 00:09:35,208
YOU WOULD NOT HAVE THE TOOLS
TO EXPRESS THAT KNOWLEDGE.

117
00:09:35,291 --> 00:09:39,208
I DO NOT BELONG
TO THE WORLD.

118
00:09:39,291 --> 00:09:41,125
THAT IS THE LIMIT,

119
00:09:41,208 --> 00:09:44,708
THE BOUNDARY
BETWEEN ALL AND SELF.

120
00:09:44,791 --> 00:09:47,708
- WELL, I WAS THERE
BECAUSE I WAS TOLD

121
00:09:47,791 --> 00:09:50,458
THAT SOMEONE REPORTED
AN INFECTED AUTOREIV.

122
00:09:50,541 --> 00:09:52,041
- INCORRECT.

123
00:09:52,125 --> 00:09:56,000
IT IS NOT
"I THINK THEREFORE I AM."

124
00:09:56,083 --> 00:09:58,000
- BUT I'M NOT LYING.

125
00:09:58,083 --> 00:10:00,791
IF YOU TAKE A LOOK
AT THE FACILITY'S RECORDS...

126
00:10:00,875 --> 00:10:02,625
- CORRECT.

127
00:10:02,708 --> 00:10:05,250
THE ANSWER IS,
"I THINK THEREFORE YOU ARE."

128
00:10:05,333 --> 00:10:08,250
YOU STILL DON'T REMEMBER,
DO YOU?

129
00:10:08,333 --> 00:10:10,833
- HOLD ON.
YOU KNOW, DON'T YOU?

130
00:10:10,916 --> 00:10:13,875
PLEASE TELL ME
WHAT THE PROXY IS.

131
00:10:13,958 --> 00:10:16,208
TELL ME ABOUT THE MONSTER.

132
00:10:16,291 --> 00:10:18,750
- YOU THINK PROXIES
ARE MONSTERS?

133
00:10:18,833 --> 00:10:20,416
( laughs )

134
00:10:20,500 --> 00:10:22,250
YOU DON'T KNOW MUCH
ABOUT ANYTHING.

135
00:10:22,333 --> 00:10:24,708
PEOPLE HAVE CALLED THEM
MONSTERS OR DEMONS, BUT THAT'S--

136
00:10:24,791 --> 00:10:26,916
- RE-L!
- --ALL NOTHING BUT NONSENSE.

137
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:28,708
IN TRUTH, PROXIES ARE-- 
- YOU!

138
00:10:28,791 --> 00:10:31,250
- THEY HAVE THE POWER
TO CHANGE THEIR APPEARANCE

139
00:10:31,333 --> 00:10:34,500
INTO ANY FORM THEY CHOOSE.
THEY CAN DISAPPEAR WITH EASE,

140
00:10:34,583 --> 00:10:36,541
LEAVING NO TRACE
THEY WERE EVER THERE.

141
00:10:36,625 --> 00:10:38,291
- IT'S ALL ABOUT YOU.

142
00:10:38,375 --> 00:10:40,333
- THEY CAN ALSO
ENTER HUMAN BEINGS

143
00:10:40,416 --> 00:10:42,916
AND TAKE CONTROL
OF THEIR MIND AND BODY.

144
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:44,625
- IT'S WHAT YOU ARE.

145
00:10:44,708 --> 00:10:46,208
- THEY CAN
SUMMON LIGHTENING BOLTS

146
00:10:46,291 --> 00:10:48,416
AND SCORCH THE EARTH
WITH THEIR POWER.

147
00:10:48,500 --> 00:10:50,250
- IT'S TIME TO REMEMBER.

148
00:10:50,333 --> 00:10:52,583
- THEY CAN EVEN CONJURE UP
PLANETS FROM THE SKY!

149
00:10:52,666 --> 00:10:54,791
- ERGO PROXY!
- STOP IT!

150
00:10:54,875 --> 00:10:57,583
NO, I'M NOT!
I'M VINCENT LAW!

151
00:11:12,625 --> 00:11:16,916
REGISTRATION #0724FGARK.

152
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:18,916
MY NAME IS VINCENT LAW.

153
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:29,916
- IT SEEMS
YOU REALLY ARE A FOOL.

154
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:32,916
HAVE YOU LOST YOUR EYE
FOR THE TRUTH

155
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:34,291
AS WELL AS YOUR MEMORY?

156
00:11:34,375 --> 00:11:36,083
- MY MEMORY?

157
00:11:36,166 --> 00:11:38,333
I HAVE NO PROBLEM
WITH MY MEMORY.

158
00:11:38,416 --> 00:11:40,708
- WELL, THEN WHO ARE YOU?

159
00:11:40,791 --> 00:11:42,750
TRY AND TELL ME
WHO YOU REALLY ARE.

160
00:11:42,833 --> 00:11:44,750
( chuckles )

161
00:11:44,833 --> 00:11:46,875
- I'M--

162
00:11:51,708 --> 00:11:54,125
AFTER I IMMIGRATED
TO ROMDEAU,

163
00:11:54,208 --> 00:11:59,083
I GOT A STAFF JOB AT THE
AUTOREIV DISPOSAL UNIT FACILITY.

164
00:11:59,166 --> 00:12:00,500
- AND BEFORE THAT?

165
00:12:01,666 --> 00:12:03,583
- I WAS LOOKING FOR WORK

166
00:12:03,666 --> 00:12:06,458
IN THE F.G. TEMPORARY
IMMIGRANT DISTRICT.

167
00:12:06,541 --> 00:12:09,416
THAT'S WHERE I FIRST SAW RE-L.

168
00:12:11,916 --> 00:12:13,500
- AND BEFORE THAT?

169
00:12:14,791 --> 00:12:17,125
- BEFORE I IMMIGRATED
TO ROMDEAU,

170
00:12:17,208 --> 00:12:20,000
I LIVED
IN THE DOME CITY OF MOSK.

171
00:12:20,083 --> 00:12:21,791
THERE WAS AN ACCIDENT.

172
00:12:21,875 --> 00:12:24,125
THE CITY WAS DESTROYED.

173
00:12:24,208 --> 00:12:25,833
IT WAS HORRIBLE.

174
00:12:25,916 --> 00:12:27,250
- AND BEFORE THAT?

175
00:12:28,458 --> 00:12:31,000
- I WAS IN MOSK.

176
00:12:32,916 --> 00:12:34,958
- AND WHAT HAPPENED THERE?

177
00:12:35,041 --> 00:12:37,791
- IT WAS A LONG TIME AGO.

178
00:12:37,875 --> 00:12:39,333
- WHAT HAPPENED?

179
00:12:39,416 --> 00:12:41,541
- I CAN'T REMEMBER.

180
00:12:44,416 --> 00:12:48,375
- YOU CAN'T REMEMBER BECAUSE YOU
STILL DON'T WANT TO REMEMBER.

181
00:12:48,458 --> 00:12:51,583
LET'S SEE WHAT QUESTIONS
YOU CAN ANSWER.

182
00:12:51,666 --> 00:12:53,041
- ( shattering )

183
00:12:55,708 --> 00:12:57,958
- IF YOU CAN'T FIND
THE ANSWER YOURSELF,

184
00:12:58,041 --> 00:13:00,125
THEN ASKING ME
IS POINTLESS.

185
00:13:00,208 --> 00:13:03,000
YOU'RE NOT CAPABLE
OF UNDERSTANDING YET.

186
00:13:03,083 --> 00:13:04,750
- WHY? 
- I'VE TOLD YOU.

187
00:13:04,833 --> 00:13:07,166
IT'S BECAUSE A PART OF YOU,
VINCENT--

188
00:13:07,250 --> 00:13:10,250
OBSERVE.

189
00:13:10,333 --> 00:13:12,208
- Vincent:
NO.  I'M--

190
00:13:12,291 --> 00:13:14,875
- ( fingers snap )

191
00:13:14,958 --> 00:13:17,166
- --DREAMING.

192
00:13:17,250 --> 00:13:21,083
- THIS IS NOT A DREAM,
VINCENT LAW.

193
00:13:29,625 --> 00:13:32,000
- Bookkeeper: THE MOST
IMPORTANT PART OF A BOOKSTORE

194
00:13:32,083 --> 00:13:34,041
IS, OF COURSE, THE BOOKS.

195
00:13:34,125 --> 00:13:37,291
THERE IS A MAGIC INHERENT
IN LANGUAGE.

196
00:13:37,375 --> 00:13:39,958
OUR WORLD IS RULED
BY LOGOS.

197
00:13:40,041 --> 00:13:44,291
SOME WORDS CONTAIN THEIR
OWN INTERNAL CONTRADICTIONS.

198
00:13:44,375 --> 00:13:48,916
FROM THESE OPPOSITIONS,
GREAT TRUTHS CAN BE REVEALED.

199
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:52,208
BIOS, FOR EXAMPLE.

200
00:13:52,291 --> 00:13:56,875
THE WORD "BIOS" CAN BE DEFINED
AS THE PROCESS OF LIFE,

201
00:13:56,958 --> 00:14:00,708
OR AS THE ARCHER'S BOW.

202
00:14:00,791 --> 00:14:05,000
THE BOW AND LIFE-- AT FIRST,
THEY SEEM QUITE UNRELATED.

203
00:14:05,083 --> 00:14:08,583
BUT BOTH INEVITABLY RESULT
IN DEATH.

204
00:14:08,666 --> 00:14:13,000
THE PHILOSOPHERS OF THE ANCIENT
WORLD COULD BE VERY CLEVER.

205
00:14:13,083 --> 00:14:14,458
- YEAH.

206
00:14:16,083 --> 00:14:19,000
- "ANAMNESIS."

207
00:14:19,083 --> 00:14:21,000
THE WORD HAS TWO MEANINGS,

208
00:14:21,083 --> 00:14:25,000
BOTH MEMORY AND RECOLLECTION.

209
00:14:25,083 --> 00:14:27,083
- Male voice:
REMEMBRANCE.

210
00:14:27,166 --> 00:14:29,416
WHO WAS VINCENT LAW?

211
00:14:29,500 --> 00:14:31,541
WHAT WAS HE AFRAID OF?

212
00:14:31,625 --> 00:14:34,250
WHAT DID HE DECIDE
TO ERASE HERE?

213
00:14:34,333 --> 00:14:37,208
- ( snaps )

214
00:14:40,333 --> 00:14:43,583
- I PRESENT A TIME
OF DESTRUCTION.

215
00:14:43,666 --> 00:14:45,833
THERE IS MISFORTUNE
IN THE STARS.

216
00:14:45,916 --> 00:14:49,125
THE SKY IS LOST
AND THE SEA IS FROZEN OVER.

217
00:14:49,208 --> 00:14:53,791
THE CIRCLE OF LIFE
WHICH ALLOW BOTH MAN

218
00:14:53,875 --> 00:14:58,041
AND NATURE TO FLOURISH
HAVE ALL BUT STOPPED.

219
00:14:58,125 --> 00:15:02,291
THE MAIN PLAYERS OF OUR STORY
HAVE LONG SINCE LEFT THE STAGE.

220
00:15:02,375 --> 00:15:07,041
WE HANG IN ANTICIPATION FOR
THE INEVITABLE FINAL CURTAIN.

221
00:15:07,125 --> 00:15:11,125
AND YET,
EVEN AT THIS LATE HOUR,

222
00:15:11,208 --> 00:15:15,291
TRACES OF THE GREAT CIRCLE
REMAIN.

223
00:15:15,375 --> 00:15:18,541
THE CIRCLE OF LIFE

224
00:15:18,625 --> 00:15:23,458
ONLY CONTINUES
BECAUSE YOU EXIST.

225
00:15:23,541 --> 00:15:27,375
WE WAIT TO SEE THE FATE
OF YOU LAST SURVIVORS

226
00:15:27,458 --> 00:15:30,791
OF THIS WORLD,
FOR IF YOU PERISH,

227
00:15:30,875 --> 00:15:33,208
PERCEPTION IS REMOVED

228
00:15:33,291 --> 00:15:37,041
AND EXISTENCE
COMES TO AN END.

229
00:15:37,125 --> 00:15:39,041
A UNIVERSE WITHOUT PERCEPTION

230
00:15:39,125 --> 00:15:41,666
IS MUCH LIKE AN ENORMOUS
STACK OF ROTTING BOOKS,

231
00:15:41,750 --> 00:15:44,541
FOREVER UNOPENED
AND UNREAD.

232
00:15:44,625 --> 00:15:47,333
- STOP IT.
PLEASE STOP.

233
00:15:47,416 --> 00:15:50,833
- TO SURVIVE THIS DARKNESS,
THE UNIVERSE HAS THRUST ITSELF

234
00:15:50,916 --> 00:15:53,500
INTO A NEXT PHASE
OF ITS LIFE CYCLE.

235
